    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The primary validation evidence (RH index comparison across 5 operating points, MAPE 12.4%, maximum deviation 18%) satisfies the pre-specified acceptance criterion. Supporting validation results for pump pressure rise and wall shear stress distribution provide additional confidence in model fidelity. The credibility assessment team unanimously accepts the CFD model as fit for the stated COU.",
